                <text class="content"><text style="font-size: 15pt;">一、失眠\n</text><text style="font-size: 13pt;">定义</text>：最常见的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">睡眠</text>障碍\n\n<text style="font-size: 13pt;">基本方式</text>：\n①<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">入睡</text>困难\n②<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">保持睡意</text>困难\n③持续<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">早醒</text>\n\n<text style="font-size: 13pt;">影响</text>：失眠是极其痛苦的，不仅如此，失眠还和白天的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">困倦</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">认知</text>功能受损、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">抑郁</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">焦虑</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">滥用药物</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">高血压</text>和许多健康问题有关\n\n<text style="font-size: 13pt;">病因</text>：\n①<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">情绪问题</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">高度应激</text>的副作用：如过度<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">紧张</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">焦虑</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">背部疼痛</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">溃疡</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">哮踹</text>等健康问题会导致<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">入睡</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">保持睡眠</text>困难\n②<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">刺激性药物</text>：一些<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">毒品</text>的使用会导致睡眠问题\n③<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">过度觉醒模型</text>：一些人拥有更高的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">生理觉醒</text>水平，倾向于表现出<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">心率</text>上升、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">新陈代谢</text>加快、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">体温</text>升高、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">促觉醒</text>的激素分泌和觉醒相关的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">脑电波</text>\n\n<text style="font-size: 13pt;">治疗</text>：\n药物治疗\n使用苯二氮类镇静剂：<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">盐酸氟胺安定</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">酣乐欣</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">替马西泮</text>\n使用非苯二氮类镇静剂：<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">安必恩</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">索纳塔</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">舒乐安定</text>\n<text style="font-size: 13pt;">缺点</text>：\n①不适合作为失眠的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">长期</text>解决方案，由于镇静剂有使人<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">困倦</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">迟钝</text>的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">延滞</text>效应，并会<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">损害</text>正常功能\n②镇静剂的持续使用会导致<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">耐药型</text>增加、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">药效</text>下降而不得不提升药量，从而造成药物<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">依赖</text>上升和白天<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">困倦</text>的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">恶性循环</text>，当停止用药，失眠程度会增加并且会体验到令人不适的停药症状。\n<text style="font-size: 13pt;">其他方法</text>：\n养成良好的生活习惯、减少<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">兴奋剂</text>（如<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">咖啡因</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">尼古丁</text>）的摄入、睡前避免<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">反复沉思</text>\n\n<text style="font-size: 15pt;">二、睡眠障碍\n</text>①<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">睡眠呼吸中止症</text>：是指睡眠中<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">频繁</text>或<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">反射性</text>急需<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">氧气</text>从而<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">惊醒</text>的症状，通常伴随较大的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">鼾声</text>；睡眠呼吸中止对睡眠产生中断效应导致白天过度<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">困倦</text>，不仅如此，它使得过度<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">紧张</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">冠心病</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">中风</text>的易感性提高。一项研究发现严重的睡眠呼吸中止症将个人<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">死亡风险</text>提高3倍。\n②<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">噩梦</text>：是指一些引起焦虑、致人惊醒的梦，通常发生在<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">REM睡眠</text>阶段；\n③<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">夜惊</text>：从<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">非快速眼动睡眠</text>中惊醒并伴随强烈<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">自主唤起</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">恐慌惨叫</text>，一般发生在睡眠<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">早期</text>\n④<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">夜游症</text>：睡眠状态中起身并四处漫游，通常发生在<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">睡眠前</text>3个小时，处于<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">慢波睡眠</text>状态\n⑤<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">快速眼动睡眠行为障碍</text>：快速眼动期潜在困扰的梦呓，梦呓可能变得极其<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">暴力</text>，其病因和某种负责快速眼动期<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">静息</text>状态的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">脑干</text>结构损伤有关\n\n<text style="font-size: 15pt;">三、精神药物:\n</text>①<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">鸦片制剂</text>：是取自鸦片的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">镇痛</text>药物，如<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">海洛因</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">吗啡</text>等，副作用是<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">嗜睡</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">恶心</text>以及心理和运动功能<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">受损</text>\n②<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">镇静剂</text>：是用于降低<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">中枢神经系统CNS</text>活性和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">行为</text>活性从而诱发<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">睡意</text>的药物，如<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">酒精</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">巴比妥盐酸</text>等，副作用是<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">困倦</text>、不可以预知的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">情绪</text>波动、心理功能<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">严重</text>受损\n③<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">兴奋剂</text>：用于<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">提升</text>CNS活性和行为活性的药物，如<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">可卡因</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">安非他命</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">尼古丁</text>等，副作用是<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">多动</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">焦虑</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">惊恐</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">失眠</text>\n④<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">致幻剂</text>：能够使感觉和知觉体验<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">扭曲</text>的药物，如<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">LSD</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">摇头丸</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">大麻</text>等，副作用是会严重损害<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">判断</text>以及产生<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">混乱</text>的思维过程\n\n<text style="font-size: 15pt;">四、冥想\n</text><text style="font-size: 13pt;">定义</text>：冥想是指一系列训练注意力从而提高<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">觉察</text>水平，并使得心理过程更加受到<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">自主</text>控制的练习\n<text style="font-size: 13pt;">种类</text>：\n①<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">集中式注意方法</text>：注意力被集中于特定<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">物体</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">画面</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">声音</text>或<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">身体感觉</text>，目的是<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">厘清</text>大脑的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">混乱</text>\n②<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">开放式检测方法</text>：注意指向个人<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">即时即地</text>的体验而不予<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">体验</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">反应</text>，目的在于能<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">超脱</text>地观察自己的<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">感官</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">思想</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">情绪</text>。<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">正念冥想</text>是开放式检测的一种\n<text style="font-size: 13pt;">作用</text>：\n①研究表明，冥想者<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">心率</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">皮电</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">呼吸率</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">耗氧量</text>均下降，表明冥想引导了一种抑制<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">生理觉醒</text>的、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">潜在有益</text>的生理状态。同时，冥想能够帮助<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">控制血压</text>、<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">增强心脏健康</text>和<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">提高睡眠节律</text>\n②研究表明，冥想可能对于减少<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">压力</text>、提高<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">免疫力</text>有长期价值；能增强心理健康的同时降低<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">焦虑</text>水平和防止<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">滥用药物</text>\n③冥想能够提高<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">注意力</text>、提高<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">觉知</text>、构建<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">情绪恢复</text>以及培养<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">成熟道德</text>。\n④冥想能够通过改变<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">意识</text>状态或<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">大脑</text>结构提高个体对<text style="color: red; opacity: {{xianshi}};">疼痛</text>的忍受力</text>
